   PORT HURON, Mich. -- Southeastern Michigan Gas Enterprises
Inc. said Semco Pipeline Co. received authorization to
construct an extension and operate its Eaton Rapids pipeline.
   The pipeline will allow Semco to transport gas from the
Eaton Rapids Gas Storage System to storage customers.
</LP>
