   The Michigan Public Service Commission has authorized the
issuance of as much as $24 million in long-term debt by the
Eaton Rapids Gas Storage System. Proceeds of the debt will be
used to refinance short-term debt incurred for the
acquisition of property and construction of facilities for
the storage system.
