</SO>
<CO>
   OG
</CO>
<LP>
   NEW YORK -- Ogden Corp. said its Ogden Allied Services
Corp. unit and Universal Services, a Seattle-based remote
services concern, have formed a joint venture, Universal
Ogden Services.
   Ogden said the company, to be based in Seattle, will be
one of the largest remote services companies in the U.S.,
providing catering, housekeeping and other services to
hundreds of offshore and other secluded locations throughout
the U.S., Canada and Europe.
